# Per-seed full per-step loss traces are large (~1.2 MB each at m=8); kept
# locally for inspection but not committed. The compact endpoint cells
# (seed_<NNN>.json) and the rolled-up seed_sweep.json ARE committed.
**/_runs/**/*_trace.json
# Dispatcher job logs + heartbeat are ephemeral run state.
**/_runs/**/*.log
_progress.json
# crossover claim-locks (ephemeral)
**/_runs/**/*.claim
